{
  "id": "69c451bcb1bb6f4d72c4de3b",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:見せかけの生産性",
  "created": 1774473662,
  "updated": 1774473937,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c451bcb1bb6f4d72c4de3b",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:見せかけの生産性",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473662,
      "updated": 1774473662
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451be0000000000c6c68b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473662,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c68c",
      "text": "はいはーい！今日のテーマは「[見せかけの生産性]」だよ〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c68d",
      "text": "なんかさ、めっちゃ頑張ってる“っぽい”のに、あとで「何も進んでなくね？」ってなるやつw あるあるすぎて草なんだけどw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c68e",
      "text": "じゃ、まずあやねーどう思う〜？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c68f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c690",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c691",
      "text": "そうねぇ……「忙しさ」という衣をまとった静かな停滞、とでも申しましょうか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c692",
      "text": "一生懸命に手を動かしているのに、心の奥では何も積み上がっていないような……そんな空虚さを、時折感じることがありますわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c693",
      "text": "本を読んでいても、ただ頁をめくることに満足してしまい、内容が心に残らないような……（少し考える）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c694",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c695",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c696",
      "text": "うわ、それわかる〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c697",
      "text": "ノートめっちゃキレイにまとめて「やった感」出るけど、テストで「あれ？知らん…」ってなるやつw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c698",
      "text": "あれ完全に“やってる風”だよねw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c699",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c69a",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c69b",
      "text": "それは典型的な「アウトプット不在型インプット」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c69c",
      "text": "学習科学では、受動的な処理は記憶定着率が低いとされている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c69d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c69e",
      "text": "要するに、「やった気になる行動」と「実際に成果が出る行動」は別物。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c69f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6a0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6a1",
      "text": "出た、りかの専門用語w",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6a2",
      "text": "つまりさ、「勉強してる気分」だけじゃダメってことだよね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6a3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6a4",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6a5",
      "text": "その理解で問題ない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6a6",
      "text": "さらに言うと、人間は「可視化された努力」に快感を覚える。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6a7",
      "text": "例えば、チェックリストを埋める、ノートを装飾する、長時間机に向かう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6a8",
      "text": "これらは“努力の演出”として機能するが、本質的な進捗とは無関係な場合がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6aa",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ab",
      "text": "まるで舞台の上で、懸命に演じている役者のようですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ac",
      "text": "観客には熱意が伝わるけれど、物語そのものは前へ進んでいない……そんな印象を受けます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ad",
      "text": "けれど、その努力も決して無意味とは言い切れないのではないかしら。心の支えになることもありますもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6af",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6b0",
      "text": "あ〜それもわかる！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6b1",
      "text": "「今日は頑張った！」って思えないと、やる気バフ切れるしねw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6b2",
      "text": "でもさ、それに甘えてずっと“雰囲気ガチ勢”になるのはヤバくない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6b3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6b4",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6b5",
      "text": "的確。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6b6",
      "text": "重要なのは「自己満足」と「実質的成果」のバランス。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6b7",
      "text": "短期的にはモチベーション維持として有効だが、長期的には最適化が必要。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6b8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6b9",
      "text": "要点整理：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ba",
      "text": " 見せかけの生産性＝進捗が伴わない努力の演出",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6bb",
      "text": " 心理的報酬はある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6bc",
      "text": " しかし成果には直結しない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6bd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6be",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6bf",
      "text": "（微笑）りかさんのまとめは、まるで地図のようで安心いたしますわ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6c0",
      "text": "けれど……人はなぜ、そのような“演出”に惹かれてしまうのでしょうね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6c2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6c3",
      "text": "え、たぶん楽だからじゃない？w",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6c4",
      "text": "ガチで考えるのってカロリー高いし、ノート書いてる方が楽しいしw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6c5",
      "text": "あと「やってる自分えらい！」って思えるしw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6c7",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6c8",
      "text": "補足すると、「認知的負荷回避」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6c9",
      "text": "人間は難しい課題よりも、処理しやすいタスクを選ぶ傾向がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ca",
      "text": "つまり、“簡単に達成感が得られる行動”に流れる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6cb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6cc",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6cd",
      "text": "なるほど……努力のように見えて、実は心を守るための優しさでもあるのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ce",
      "text": "けれど、その優しさが未来の自分を苦しめることもある……少し切ないですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6d0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6d1",
      "text": "うっ、それ言われると刺さるw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6d2",
      "text": "未来のテストの自分、ごめんってなるやつw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6d3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6d4",
      "text": "じゃあさ、どうすれば“ガチの生産性”になるの？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6d5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6d6",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6d7",
      "text": "結論から言う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6d8",
      "text": "「アウトプットを基準にすること」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6da",
      "text": "例えば：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6db",
      "text": " 説明できるか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6dc",
      "text": " 問題を解けるか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6dd",
      "text": " 何かを作れるか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6de",
      "text": "この3つが満たされれば、実質的な進捗とみなせる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6df",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6e0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6e1",
      "text": "おお〜、つまり「できるかどうか」が全てって感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6e2",
      "text": "ゲームで言うと、チュートリアル読んだだけじゃクリアにならない的なw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6e3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6e4",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6e5",
      "text": "適切な比喩。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6e6",
      "text": "実践＝クリア条件。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6e8",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6e9",
      "text": "（小さく笑う）ゲームにたとえると、とても分かりやすいですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ea",
      "text": "わたくしも、ただ本を読むだけでなく、感想を書いたり、人に語ったりしてみようかしら。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6eb",
      "text": "そうすれば、物語がより深く心に根づく気がいたします。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ed",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ee",
      "text": "いいじゃんそれ！アウトプット女子w",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ef",
      "text": "じゃあ今日のまとめいくよ〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6f0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6f1",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（まとめ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6f2",
      "text": " 「見せかけの生産性」＝やってる感だけで中身スカスカなやつ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6f3",
      "text": " 人はラクで気持ちいい方に流れがち",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6f4",
      "text": " でも「できるようになったか？」がガチ指標！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6f5",
      "text": "って感じかな〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6f7",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6f8",
      "text": "補足。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6f9",
      "text": "「演出を完全に捨てる必要はない。ただし、支配されるな。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6fa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6fb",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6fc",
      "text": "（微笑）まるで物語の一節のようですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6fd",
      "text": "わたくしたちも、自分自身の物語を、確かな歩みで紡いでいきたいものです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6fe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c6ff",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c700",
      "text": "おお、なんかいい感じに締まったw",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c451bf0000000000c6c701",
      "text": "じゃ、今日はここまで！おつ〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473663,
      "updated": 1774473663
    },
    {
      "id": "69c452c40000000000c6c702",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473925,
      "updated": 1774473925
    },
    {
      "id": "69c452c50000000000c6c703",
      "text": "#2026-03-26",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473925,
      "updated": 1774473937
    },
    {
      "id": "69c452c60000000000c6c704",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774473926,
      "updated": 1774473926
    }
  ]
}